---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import GetInTouchBanner from "../../components/common/GetInTouchBanner.tsx";
---

<BaseLayout title="Abigail Joseph – NAG Project - BBSD">
  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative h-[60vh] min-h-[400px] w-full overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="/images/projects/nag-project.jpg"
        alt=""
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50"></div>
      <div
        class="relative z-10 flex h-full flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 text-center"
      >
        <p class="mb-2 text-xs tracking-widest text-white/60 uppercase">
          [ PROJECT ]
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white md:text-6xl">
          Abigail Joseph – NAG Project
        </h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Project Info -->
    <section class="bg-white py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-6">
        <!-- Meta -->
        <div
          class="mb-12 grid gap-4 border-b border-gray-light/20 pb-8 sm:grid-cols-3"
        >
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-gray-light uppercase"
            >
              Project
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-dark">
              Abigail Joseph – NAG Project
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-gray-light uppercase"
            >
              Client
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-dark">
              Yinson / Jord Oil & Gas
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-gray-light uppercase"
            >
              Year
            </p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-dark">2024.11 to 2026.4</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BBSD Services -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-lg font-bold text-dark">BBSD Services:</h2>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="/services/procurement"
              class="rounded-full bg-blue-light px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-blue-dark transition-colors hover:bg-blue-dark hover:text-white"
              >Project Procurement Services</a
            >
            <a
              href="/services/engineering"
              class="rounded-full bg-blue-light px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-blue-dark transition-colors hover:bg-blue-dark hover:text-white"
              >Topside Module Details Design Services - Structure/Piping/E&I</a
            >
            <a
              href="/services"
              class="rounded-full bg-blue-light px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-blue-dark transition-colors hover:bg-blue-dark hover:text-white"
              >Topside Module Construction – Site Supervision Services</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Description -->
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-lg font-bold text-dark">Project Description:</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray">
            <p>
              The FPSO Abigail Joseph, the facility required for treatment of
              these hydrocarbons (Oil & Gas), has capacity constraints to
              handling the expected oil and gas rates. A new NAG (Non-Associated
              Gas) module is required, and a debottlenecking activity is to be
              carried out on FPSO AJ to enable her to handle these increased
              rates for phase 1.
            </p>
            <p>
              The NAG Upgrade Project includes installation and integration of a
              new build process module, containing equipment and systems for NAG
              reception, separation & conditioning, water treatment and gas
              compression & export metering. The new module shall be designed
              and installed such that the gas production of the Abigail Joseph
              FPSO shall increase from the original design capacity.
            </p>
            <p>
              BBSD is awarded orders by Jord Oil & Gas for the tasks as below:
            </p>
            <ol class="list-inside list-decimal space-y-2 pl-2">
              <li>
                Support project procurements in China including piping bulk
                materials, Electrical Cables, and other instruments.
              </li>
              <li>
                Engineering Services to support details design for Structure,
                E&I, and Piping disciplines.
              </li>
              <li>
                Supply professional team members for all disciplines to the
                construction site for site supervision services.
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a
            href="/projects"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-dark px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-dark/80"
            >MORE PROJECTS</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <GetInTouchBanner client:visible />
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
